   Iraq 21,284
   Kuwait 308,177
   Saudi Arabia 147,549
   Other Persian Gulf States 64,037
   Libya 23,759
   United States 108,045
   Other non-Arab countries 143,780
   Other Arab countries: 52,683
   Total: 4,739,158
